query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('absolute-value',
'bash',
'boolean-algebra',
'compactness',
'contour-integration',
'coordinate-systems',
'fourier-series',
'homological-algebra',
'order-theory',
'recursion',
'unity')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Commentator',
'Custodian',
'Editor',
'Famous Question',
'Informed',
'Nice Question',
'Popular Question',
'Supporter',
'Teacher',
'Tumbleweed',
'Yearling');
